The People of the State of Illinois, Plaintiff-Appellee, v. Clifford Binder, Defendant-Appellant.(No. 59418;First District (1st Division)April 1, 1974.

GOLDBERG, J., took no part.

PER CURIAM. O’Donnell, Wolff, LeVine, Mazzorana & Krupa, of Chicago (Arthur J. O’Donnell, of counsel), for appellant. Bernard Carey, State’s Attorney, of Chicago (Patrick T. Driscoll and Mary Ellen Dienes, Assistant State’s Attorneys, of counsel), for the People.
